yarn
13. Compile Java Program

Open CMD inside project folder.

Compile:

javac -classpath "%HADOOP_HOME%\share\hadoop\common\*;%HADOOP_HOME%\share\hadoop\common\lib\*;%HADOOP_HOME%\share\hadoop\mapreduce\*;%HADOOP_HOME%\share\hadoop\hdfs\*;%HADOOP_HOME%\share\hadoop\yarn\*" -d . WordCount.java
14. Create JAR File
jar -cvf wordcount.jar *
